# Development Workflow

## Getting Started
- Install dependencies: `yarn install`
- Start development server: `yarn dev`
- Build for production: `yarn build`
- Preview production build: `yarn preview`

## Project Configuration
- Vite is configured in [vite.config.mjs](mdc:vite.config.mjs)
- Vue Router is set up in [src/router/](mdc:src/router)
- State management with Pinia in [src/stores/](mdc:src/stores)

## Component Development
- UI components use Ant Design Vue
- Create reusable components in [src/components/](mdc:src/components)
- Create page components in [src/views/](mdc:src/views)
- Use UnoCSS for utility CSS

## API Development
- API services are defined in [src/apis/](mdc:src/apis)
- Mock APIs with MSW in [src/mocks/](mdc:src/mocks)
- Real backend with Appwrite configured in [src/appwrite.js](mdc:src/appwrite.js)

## Deployment
- Deploy to Vercel using the configuration in [vercel.json](mdc:vercel.json)
- All routes are rewritten to index.html for SPA routing
- MSW is configured with special headers for the service worker
